{"tid":236172,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"一個月應該點由英文LV2操到IELTS 5.5?","createTime":"2017-05-09T13:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T04:17:43.000Z","uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2f7681e95bb27930c22cd6cf661c6614bb65d4a8","tid":236172,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"IELTS 5.5大概係LV3，英文LV2其實有冇可能一個月操到變5.5<br />\n最弱係口試，係唔係都可以操返黎?<br />\n另外有邊份卷係唔洗點重點咁操?<br />\n因為我見reading定listening好似係香港人比較強，lv2都可能有6?<br />\n但writing我知道要操<br />\n<br />\n希望一個月內可以有5.5既水平<br />\n我知好多巴絲打有8都話自己廢<br />\n但5.5對我黎講好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經上網睇左少少心得<br />\n不過冇咩lv2既人考既例子...所以想知"},{"pid":"2cff0709f56862f5b8a236fb5ecfe863c39804d8","tid":236172,"uid":88785,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"6.0先lv3 wor ching"},{"pid":"6f8817ec41b33c367db066c17fd4c6c79bf2af2e","tid":236172,"uid":109567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"我果陣英文2去考都有5.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  speaking有6添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> speaking係最易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7fda7bb06ad84504691285b987b36c840c49e5","tid":236172,"uid":45335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"2=5.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜鳩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d562e3088e92efae6f7487f9eeb53a714e48bb1a","tid":236172,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6.0先lv3 wor ching</blockquote><br />\n文憑試英國語文科等級<br />\n對應IELTS整體分數<br />\n5**\t7.51 &ndash; 7.77<br />\n5*\t7.16 &ndash; 7.32<br />\n5\t6.81 &ndash; 6.99<br />\n4\t6.31 &ndash; 6.51<br />\n3\t5.48 &ndash; 5.68<br />\n2\t4.79 &ndash; 5.07<br />\n<br />\n不過我都知唔可以直接比較"},{"pid":"3c2cca138eca2b91d10d5f2133e878330fa51f01","tid":236172,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果陣英文2去考都有5.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  speaking有6添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> speaking係最易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你speaking都係2?<br />\n因為說話比較弱...所以真係少少驚"},{"pid":"1b91ad3bcdd2cbdb18d2f74c8c0c5ba59230d74f","tid":236172,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2=5.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜鳩姐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係? 即係正常lv2去考已經有5.5架啦??"},{"pid":"e7f90835f11ed06db6f4fe0a7acf42dd0f43d3e1","tid":236172,"uid":109567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我果陣英文2去考都有5.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  speaking有6添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> speaking係最易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你speaking都係2?<br />\n因為說話比較弱...所以真係少少驚</blockquote><br />\nSpeaking係一對一 我覺得輕鬆好多<br />\n不過都係睇人 dse 2可能唔止5.5 又可能低過5.5 <br />\n你如果一定要考到5.5 咁自己準備下先考啦 唔係到時唔夠分既話哂錢哂時間再考過"},{"pid":"8ad8c099a5eb1597b7530d4eb1c5c4c895daa9e3","tid":236172,"uid":75033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"驚咩 我當年乜都冇溫 係考dse前個個2月去考 最後 5.5  dse 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我啲細分仲要係 5 5 5 6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家咪又係順利係uk頹緊考final<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bdba4726fa1d4c679358861a23854d8c12e5f27","tid":236172,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我果陣英文2去考都有5.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  speaking有6添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> speaking係最易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你speaking都係2?<br />\n因為說話比較弱...所以真係少少驚</blockquote><br />\nSpeaking係一對一 我覺得輕鬆好多<br />\n不過都係睇人 dse 2可能唔止5.5 又可能低過5.5 <br />\n你如果一定要考到5.5 咁自己準備下先考啦 唔係到時唔夠分既話哂錢哂時間再考過</blockquote><br />\n因為我見好多人反而係衰speaking<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比起grammar，係唔係帶出意思會重要d?<br />\n因為一講英文就會太著重grammar，但如果grammar錯哂就會講得好少少...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382eaba577a4183da4a7e25269d03a72d9cefa58","tid":236172,"uid":109077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚咩 我當年乜都冇溫 係考dse前個個2月去考 最後 5.5  dse 2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我啲細分仲要係 5 5 5 6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而家咪又係順利係uk頹緊考final<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁睇黎好好準備下咁5.5應該都唔係太難咋wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63f153ab7a33e7eebc6006c78bb20dc41da75d2","tid":236172,"uid":78046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:12:01.000Z","msg":"DSE - 3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n英國一年後 IELTS 7.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5f5083c98390925e4ce1285be5e1808f8ce8f6","tid":236172,"uid":75033,"like"